column2: SELECT s.ra, s.dec, theta = (#*#) / (#*s.z) , s.z, s.zErr, q = CASE WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVAB_r WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expAB_r END, phi = CASE WHEN p.lnLExp_r < p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.DeVPhi_r WHEN p.lnLExp_r > p.lnLDeV_r THEN p.expPhi_r END, p.petroMag_r, p.petroMag_u, p.fracDeV_r INTO mydb.target_galaxies1 FROM PhotoObj p JOIN SpecObj s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID WHERE s.ra BETWEEN # and # AND s.dec BETWEEN # and # AND s.class = # AND s.z < # AND s.z > #e-# AND abs (s.zErr) < #e-# AND s.zWarning = # ALTER TABLE mydb.target_galaxies1 ADD idx_num INT_IDENTITY (#, #)
